					Constellation Mapping deploys a homing lock marker that detonates on enemies
					Harmonic Surge unleashes an expanding resonant detonation
					Stellar Crescendo finale: lunar detonation, radial star burst, and full VFX cascade
					Critical hits spawn seeking lunar crystals and bonus star fragments
					'Sharp as the moon's edge at midnight 窶・a silver scalpel honed by quiet sorrow'
					'''
			}

